snippet.title: Papetura: Craft Edition - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for the Papetura physical edition, Papetura: Craft Edition. Here's a quick peek at the physical boxed edition of the action-adventure game, which includes the game, a specially designed case containing an art book, and a code to download the original game soundtrack. 

Papetura: Craft Edition will be available later in 2024 across European specialist retailers for Nintendo Switch and PS5 (PlayStation 5). The digital version of the game is out now on PC, PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
